{"tid":873764,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[你寫我錄] 跳躍生命線獨白","createTime":"2018-10-23T16:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T11:56:05.000Z","uid":171781,"like":29,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e5fdffa5bf3f2140fbd2e1542bd995feea350b28","tid":873764,"uid":171781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T16:14:46.000Z","msg":"D人成日話，時間會治療一切傷口，其實係錯架。有D傷口，即使時間過左幾耐，你都冇辦法令佢復原。因為傷口並唔係自己度，而係喺在乎你既人身上。每當我背脊痕既時候，我就知道有人就會痛。<br />\n<br />\n我唯一能夠做既 就係話俾佢聽，呢一件係火舌中煉成，花紋咁特別既衫，喺艷陽下會閃耀獨有既光芒。<br />\n<br />\n痛過了，長出既不單單係新皮嫩肉，仲有堅強。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/jigglypuffmaster/life1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fjigglypuffmaster%2Flife1&d=VMMT7VfUgXsw4kN%2BPSsiDTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=dd20c099\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/jigglypuffmaster/life1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎巴絲打們接力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bab12716ec26ed2c15910d5670fdb88dc6feae8","tid":873764,"uid":104171,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T16:26:41.000Z","msg":"蚊香蛙咁嘅聲架咩"},{"pid":"88561c285b49c2b3c62dd70b01bd78f79598a2e1","tid":873764,"uid":171781,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T16:37:50.000Z","msg":"香港人係善忘架，但係每一次打風，總會有人提起溫黛。即使已經過左半個世紀，依然冇辦法忘記，咁係因為嗰種摧毀實在太深刻。正如今次，又會有人因為颱風花渡  而記住呢一晚。我地唔係唔想忘記，而係無法忘記。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>唔係每一句對唔住，都可以有一句原諒黎結尾架。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/jigglypuffmaster/life2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fjigglypuffmaster%2Flife2&d=VMMT7VfUgXsw4kN%2BPSsiDTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=97b9b7ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/jigglypuffmaster/life2</a>"},{"pid":"60769ed758b07df780bb704a94e403d793d8bfab","tid":873764,"uid":179990,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T16:38:03.000Z","msg":"把聲有啲似林海峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d71d82370f38348bd39fd0dc28983db933d79b8","tid":873764,"uid":171781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T23:57:02.000Z","msg":"巴絲們早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f0b5aff804c547526365d2f280962bb33ab18c","tid":873764,"uid":171781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60769ed758b07df780bb704a94e403d793d8bfab","tid":873764,"uid":179990,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T16:38:03.000Z","msg":"把聲有啲似林海峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T09:13:38.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔鐘意林海峰但都多謝你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d2cc849b1a9f373cec08eeab4c12096c397e7e","tid":873764,"uid":171781,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:51:35.000Z","msg":"每日 我們都會遇到好多人。每個人既出現，都有住佢既意義。有 D 會成為戀人知己，有 D 會成為摯友良朋。佢地既出現，係為左考驗你，為左扶助你。更多時，係為左帶出最好既你。<br />\n<br />\n每個相遇都足以影響一生。<strong>而喺相遇同相分之間，我地齊齊上左一課，學識左被愛，懂得去愛。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/jigglypuffmaster/recording-3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fjigglypuffmaster%2Frecording-3&d=VMMT7VfUgXsw4kN%2BPSsiDTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=8b57c4cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/jigglypuffmaster/recording-3</a>"},{"pid":"8f9e948c6edfebe05819c90141f9dca54e989d81","tid":873764,"uid":82570,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:41:40.000Z","msg":"我個人並不挺喜歡和陌生女孩上床。當然，這種解決性慾的方法是相當輕鬆，擁抱、愛撫本身也十分愉快，令我厭惡的是翌日早晨分手的時候，一睜開眼睛，發現身旁有個女孩正呼呼大睡，房裡充斥著一股酒味，不論是床、燈或窗，所有的擺設都透著一股賓館特有的俗氣，而我則因宿醉昏沉沉地。"},{"pid":"764594b95130aac35121ba956490b1e0b65a722e","tid":873764,"uid":171781,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8f9e948c6edfebe05819c90141f9dca54e989d81","tid":873764,"uid":82570,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:41:40.000Z","msg":"我個人並不挺喜歡和陌生女孩上床。當然，這種解決性慾的方法是相當輕鬆，擁抱、愛撫本