去買個白汁 咁d飯有d雞皇 就$26蚊<br />\n<br />\n條友問我要唔要加飲野黎飲 我唔洗講啦 就要百事 點知佢話百事有可樂<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知佢up咩鳩 跟住我話唔要野飲 佢話30蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我話唔要 跟住佢話我係咪睇電視<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6fcab8736c9af4c2a6cd42487e9435bd21e406","tid":873764,"uid":171781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:01:05.000Z","msg":"人 總係會有一刻<br />\n你以為失去所有既同時 竟然會係前所未有既得著<br />\n乜野係可以捨棄? 乜野係不能放手?<br />\n迷惘過後  緊隨既  會係一顆澄明既心<br />\n<strong>傷痛過後  換黎既  會係更堅定既人生</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/jigglypuffmaster/life5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fjigglypuffmaster%2Flife5&d=VMMT7VfUgXsw4kN%2BPSsiDTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=8dd37616\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/jigglypuffmaster/life5</a>"},{"pid":"d3d8e2d092b2727a876d094d74f3fc1ac8c7dd5b","tid":873764,"uid":171781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a1ea1d9433bcb7079d21c554a0700af6f0df958","tid":873764,"uid":144063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T15:45:58.000Z","msg":"我叫左去買個白汁 咁d飯有d雞皇 就$26蚊<br />\n<br />\n條友問我要唔要加飲野黎飲 我唔洗講啦 就要百事 點知佢話百事有可樂<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知佢up咩鳩 跟住我話唔要野飲 佢話30蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我話唔要 跟住佢話我係咪睇電視<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:06:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/jigglypuffmaster/chickenrice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fjigglypuffmaster%2Fchickenrice&d=VMMT7VfUgXsw4kN%2BPSsiDTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5fdbe981\" 