 />\n經過呢一晚 所有野已經得到答案<br />\n望住我沾滿鮮血既雙手 我發現<br />\n自己從來唔係一個救護員 而係一個法醫<br />\n到最後 原來又係一場夢 返到局我始終都係一個救護員"},{"pid":"3101f97dba3c15e739043dae32a2d1b6f16f929b","tid":873764,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:28:13.000Z","msg":"到底點解 有人要濫用救護服務呢？<br />\n我曾經聽人講過<br />\n去廁所無晒廁紙 洗頭無晒洗頭水<br />\n到頭來 都係要call十字車<br />\n壓力 從來都係我地救護員需要面對<br />\n但喺今晚 再理性既我<br />\n都要低著頭 心裏講一句<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n（但願人沒見~~~）"},{"pid":"696946b98be971ebabcc98d0d048cd1be36c7741","tid":873764,"uid":87571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"巴打好有心機<br />\n不過講嘢把聲好似冇咩感情"},{"pid":"524115fbe243961a91c3d0e331f85dfa855ed5b2","tid":873764,"uid":171781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dc1c7f5c640c3c17a9cdfd264d6b874a6a0c287","tid":873764,"uid":136729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"救護入班同操班唔難 <br />\n面對死者同家屬先至係最難"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:34:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/jigglypuffmaster/hard\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fjigglypuffmaster%2Fhard&d=VMMT7VfUgXsw4kN%2BPSsiDTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=84986922\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/jigglypuffmaster/hard</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60231fc8e61ddc0dcc7ef7249d22b4b576527c27","tid":873764,"uid":136729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"524115fbe243961a91c3d0e331f85dfa855ed5b2","tid":873764,"uid":171781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dc1c7f5c640c3c17a9cdfd264d6b874a6a0c287","tid":873764,"uid":136729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"救護入班同操班唔難 <br />\n面對死者同家屬先至係最難"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T16:34:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/jigglypuffmaster/hard\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fjigglypuffmaste